songs.title: ENCHANTÉ
songs.lyrics:
2 step, in a mess
The liquor did not fuck around
But still I’m sitting pretty
She got stardust in her eyes
She struck
She talking way too much
Just go ahead & buy my music
If you fucking with me
I ain’t got time for all that bullshit
3 dollars on my bank
& still I’m tryna push it
I’m tryna get that double cheese dog
Good shit
Then do the dash
Maybe drop a verse back in the lab
The uber price is surging
We might have to get that van
That 80 Rand is feeling like a ticket to milan
Milan
But still I’m feeling confident
Kenneth cole my boots
They made in a different continent
I know you see em
She see me & she bussdown
Like bleedem
But it’s a different season
I’m focused & all she do is tease
I think the uber’s here and all I wanna do is leave
Xoxo, I’ll see you when I see you
Enchanté
But I’m just tryna leave this place
To get to better places
I’m feeling like that loner in LA
Word to tame impala
Difference is that I’m not even in LA
I’m stuck up in the matrix
But enough about me
Trust you’ll see me soon enough on vogue magazine
She got that scarlett sweater like johansson
Vixen when she dance
She just tryna make it to the major league
Huh
In the range hanging out
These blue lights they flashing out
It’s kinda funny even when we’re in the moment
Can’t get put inside a cop car
Cause I ain’t got ID
& I just spent all of my money on pétron
Nah actually that vodka
Flowing like busta rhymes
I do this everytime
I never learn my lesson
I’m so tired of stressing
When I finally leave it’s no return ticket
No question
-
